title: Buy ETH and add liquidity for the token on major DEXes
body: Market-Buy 4 ETH, 2 will be used along with YAPE in the treasury to open liquidity pools on Uniswap and Sushiswap and 2 ETH will be kept in the DAO multisig wallet to support opening new Yapeswap pools.
choices: No - Do not open new pools
